      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ON TARGET (4) flew the lids off the inside draw with a fast early split and gave a sight, finishing a 1.3 lengths second (22.12) over 380m at this track. Makes plenty of appeal. FOOTLOOSE (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a second place finish (22.21) there the start prior. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. CONNECTICUT (1) racing well without winning, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 3rd over 380m at this track beaten 6 lengths (22.46) behind Zero Forging in a Maiden on July 17. Racing well and deserves a win. LORNA MILLY (6) is an improver in the mix despite missing out at this track when making debut.",
